Description: An implementation of an efficient DA-MCMC algorithm for conducting inference on the stochastic SIR model 
    with incidence data, which uses the piece-wise decoupled SIR process as a proposal process
    in the Metropolis-Hastings step that updates the latent data. 
    It also provides the scripts used to run the experiments conducted in the paper "A uniformly ergodic DA-MCMC for the SIR process with incidence data".
